snippet.title: Lofty Quest Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1758320/Lofty_Quest/

Itchio: https://devonwiersma.itch.io/lofty-quest

Lofty Quest is a narrative-driven hidden object adventure game where you search and explore beautiful, hand-crafted 3D dioramas to topple an evil King.
